sub_title: Senior Marketing Manager EMEA at Belkin International
summary: Results-driven marketing professional with over 10 years of experience in various marketing disciplines, including brand management, product marketing, digital marketing, trade marketing, PR/communications, and market research. Proven track record of delivering successful marketing campaigns and driving revenue growth in multinational companies across diverse industries such as FMCG, Luxury, and Technology. Strong communicator with an entrepreneurial spirit and a passion for continuous improvement and growth.
